{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, I worked for this farm of the-- of the church-- of the Catholic Church-- both in the field, and the second year, I was in-- during the winter, I was in the barn with the cows, which was warm and nice-- nice job, very nice job.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We ate very well there because they were fed in the farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And time was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing very unusual happening there until-- until one day, a German non-com in, called my name, and took me with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And took me with him to a camp that was specifically for Jewish prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they were-- they were looking for Jews all over, in every camp, in every Arbeitskommando.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were picking Jews out and taking to this camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were putting Jews together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't bide very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't a very good news because we knew that if they have us together, someday we might die together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] However, one thing is very significant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, we knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that we'll be treated much worse than being with our comrades in arms, the Polish, French, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And yet, every single Jewish prisoner that was brought into that barrack would say, thank God, I'm-- I'm on my own.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Thank God I don't have to hide anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because some of them were-- you know, have not reported that they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them have hidden their ident-- Jewish identity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were pointed out or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were hiding, you know, as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were all saying, I don't have to hide anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What happens, happens.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I lived as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never-- I was never in hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
